data.description: Uncover this remarkable residence nestled in the heart of East Port St. Lucie, perfectly situated beside a expansive canal. Located mere moments from the enchanting charm of Jensen Beach, this property presents an exceptionally distinctive coastal lifestyle.This welcoming home is a genuine gem, showcasing a peaceful waterfront setting that offers both relaxation and recreational possibilities. With convenient access to the wide canal, you can partake in boating, fishing, and tranquil moments while soaking in the scenic views.
